    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 26-08-2025</p>

    <p>Tip Jar (“the App”, “we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy. 
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the App on the Pi Network.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Pi Network Login Data:</strong> your Pi username and authentication details provided by the Pi SDK.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> basic transaction details (amount, memo, metadata) necessary to process tips through the Pi Network.</li>
      <li>We <strong>do not</strong> collect personal information beyond what is provided by Pi Network SDK.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To authenticate users via Pi Network.</li>
      <li>To process, verify, and complete Pi payments.</li>
      <li>To generate and display QR codes or shareable tip links.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>We do not store sensitive data permanently. Transaction data is verified via Pi Network APIs and not retained longer than required for payment confirmation.</p>

    <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your information with third parties. Payment verification is handled securely through official Pi Network APIs.</p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your information. However, no system is 100% secure, and we rely on Pi Network’s infrastructure for payment security.</p>

    <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>The App is not intended for children under 13.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted here.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: <a href="mailto:your@email.com">dungeonreaper26@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>
